INTRO                                             You see a plump fellow working on the dungeon walls, keeping them in repair.                                                                                                                            NAME                                              "Randy. Glad to meet you."                                                                                                                                                                              JOB                                               "Mostly fixing the dungeon, filling cracks and such. And of course, I keepeth   the FIRE of the torches smoldering."                                                                                    BYE                                               "Take care, good man."                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "Well, don't know much about that."                                                                                                                                                                     FIRE                                              "To keep light here. And keep away DARK things."                                                                                                                                                        DARK                                              "Dost thou know of dark things?"                                                                                                                                                                        YES                                               "I guess we all do."                                                                                                                                                                                    NO                                                "Then go to the dungeon where there are wells, and ask Hugh about WATER."                                                                                                                               WATER                                             "Yes, water."                                                                                                                                                                                           